  "title": "Data Inconsistency After ALTER TABLE: TiFlash Applies Stale Default Value, TiKV Correctly Uses NULL",
  "description": "## Bug Report\n\nPlease answer these questions before submitting your issue. Thanks!\n\n### 1. Minimal reproduce step (Required)\nNot sure if this is a duplicate of issue #61570, so I'm opening a new issue.\n\n```\nUSE test;\nDROP DATABASE IF EXISTS case_dyn_col_1749306107822;\nCREATE DATABASE case_dyn_col_1749306107822;\nUSE case_dyn_col_1749306107822;\nCREATE TABLE t0(c0 NUMERIC ZEROFILL DEFAULT 0.9912154622717881 , PRIMARY KEY(c0));\nALTER TABLE t0 SET TIFLASH REPLICA 1;\nALTER TABLE t0 ADD COLUMN dyn_col_1749306105328 MEDIUMINT;\nINSERT IGNORE INTO t0 (dyn_col_1749306105328) VALUES (7970226);\nALTER TABLE t0 ADD COLUMN dyn_col_1749306107472 TINYINT;\nALTER TABLE t0 DROP COLUMN dyn_col_1749306105328;\nALTER TABLE t0 ADD COLUMN dyn_col_1749306107822 DOUBLE DEFAULT 8.16158344E8;\nALTER TABLE t0 DROP COLUMN dyn_col_1749306107472;\nCREATE INDEX idx_1749306110238 ON t0 (dyn_col_1749306107822);\nALTER TABLE t0 MODIFY COLUMN dyn_col_1749306107822 DECIMAL;\nINSERT IGNORE INTO t0 (c0) VALUES (-1397511826);\nINSERT IGNORE INTO t0 (c0) VALUES (673955961);\n\nSELECT /*+ read_from_storage(tikv[t0]) */ * FROM t0;\nSELECT /*+ read_from_storage(tiflash[t0]) */ * FROM t0;\n```\n<!-- a step by step guide for reproducing the bug. -->\n\n### 2. What did you expect to see? (Required)\nThe same query returns the same results on both TiKV and TiFlash.\n### 3. What did you see instead (Required)\n```\nmysql> SELECT /*+ read_from_storage(tikv[t0]) */ * FROM t0;\n+-----------+-----------------------+\n| c0        | dyn_col_1749306107822 |\n+-----------+-----------------------+\n|         0 |                  NULL |\n| 673955961 |                  NULL |\n|         1 |             816158344 |\n+-----------+-----------------------+\n3 rows in set (0.00 sec)\n\nmysql> SELECT /*+ read_from_storage(tiflash[t0]) */ * FROM t0;\n+-----------+-----------------------+\n| c0        | dyn_col_1749306107822 |\n+-----------+-----------------------+\n|         1 |             816158344 |\n|         0 |             816158344 |\n| 673955961 |             816158344 |\n+-----------+-----------------------+\n3 rows in set (0.02 sec)\n```\nexplain info\n```\nmysql> explain SELECT /*+ read_from_storage(tikv[t0]) */ * FROM t0;\n+-----------------------+---------+-----------+----------------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+\n| id                    | estRows | task      | access object                                            | operator info                  |\n+-----------------------+---------+-----------+----------------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+\n| IndexReader_8         | 3.00    | root      |                                                          | index:IndexFullScan_7          |\n| └─IndexFullScan_7     | 3.00    | cop[tikv] | table:t0, index:idx_1749306110238(dyn_col_1749306107822) | keep order:false, stats:pseudo |\n+-----------------------+---------+-----------+----------------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+\n2 rows in set (0.00 sec)\n\nmysql> explain SELECT /*+ read_from_storage(tiflash[t0]) */ * FROM t0;\n+-------------------------+---------+--------------+---------------+--------------------------------------+\n| id                      | estRows | task         | access object | operator info                        |\n+-------------------------+---------+--------------+---------------+--------------------------------------+\n| TableReader_10          | 3.00    | root         |               | MppVersion: 2, data:ExchangeSender_9 |\n| └─ExchangeSender_9      | 3.00    | mpp[tiflash] |               | ExchangeType: PassThrough            |\n|   └─TableFullScan_8     | 3.00    | mpp[tiflash] | table:t0      | keep order:false, stats:pseudo       |\n+-------------------------+---------+--------------+---------------+--------------------------------------+\n3 rows in set (0.00 sec)\n\nmysql> select version();\n+--------------------+\n| version()          |\n+--------------------+\n| 8.0.11-TiDB-v8.5.2 |\n+--------------------+\n1 row in set (0.00 sec)\n```\n### 4. What is your TiDB version? (Required)\n\n<!-- Paste the output of SELECT tidb_version() -->\n+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+\n| tidb_version()                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |\n+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+\n| Release Version: v8.5.2\nEdition: Community\nGit Commit Hash: f43a13324440f92209e2a9f04c0bbe9cf763978d\nGit Branch: HEAD\nUTC Build Time: 2025-05-29 03:33:08\nGoVersion: go1.23.6\nRace Enabled: false\nCheck Table Before Drop: false\nStore: tikv |\n+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+",
